TITLE: Episode 74 - Welcome to Mansplain March
DESCRIPTION: Maddie and Jessie kick off women’s history month with a healthy dose of testosterone. Cam Harless of The Mad Ones and Thaddeus Preston of Thank You For Your Servers take over the episode to mansplain feminism and racism to the Vixens. This episode is not for the weak.
